{"id": "1204240543841001562", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 19, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "紅夫人，我拿來打融災4用的\n\n融災5，用紅夫人，不小心按到狂氣\n你可能自己彈死自己了", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T01:41:59.359000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["948359230199578674"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1204239182520778805", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204407423738183791", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "335963879207075840", "author_name": "yukito4577", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T12:45:06.627000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1204407423373418496", "filename": "Screenshot_20240206-204446.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 244348, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203195064474669106/1204407423373418496/Screenshot_20240206-204446.jpg?ex=69cbc1d2&is=69ca7052&hm=32f21e600c156a6f94951511c2a0833c3483566b26f27218e7d2c85d782c6416&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204407589115273216", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "335963879207075840", "author_name": "yukito4577", "author_bot": false, "content": "成功闖到王關了 想問問大佬們 有什麼出牌思路嘛", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T12:45:46.056000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204428420482596945", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "沒報償打擊時候\n生一個胚胎，給希洛拉牌\n\n其他時候，胚胎累積3_4個給雷亞吞噬回血\n\n多餘胚胎也是給這兩位補狂氣\n\n報償打擊盡量搭配希洛開大、易傷狀態時候打出去\n（特別是Boss出現回血時候）\n\n通常前兩回合，可以硬抗的話\n我會到第三回合\n他出現護盾+回血時候，一次性打掉他的血條+回血狀態\n艾繼絲的狂氣，在危險時候再放石化\n\n但要注意胚胎會全部被吃了\n\n喔！沒注意到，你沒到雷亞\n是拉蒙娜\n\n那麼就是狂氣滿，就直接拉報償打擊出來\n\n曜令滿，就一直給拉蒙娜跟希洛吃", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:08:32.641000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204428860213694496", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "有雷亞，比較好拉住血線\n\n沒雷亞，比較麻煩就是\n沒有大量回血，可以疊加耐力", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:10:17.481000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204428991998464070", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "335963879207075840", "author_name": "yukito4577", "author_bot": false, "content": "剛剛試了好幾輪 都到第二條血失敗<:843718339795877918:986589099622281216>", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:10:48.901000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204429048504389662", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "3.2萬\n希洛+易傷，報償打擊大概2萬上下", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:11:02.373000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204429142049947658", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "但，耐力少一半\n依靠回合數去回覆會很慢", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:11:24.676000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204429291660648468", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以搭雷亞，剩100血內，吃3~5\n直接回到80%血線", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:12:00.346000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204429390449213500", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "335963879207075840", "author_name": "yukito4577", "author_bot": false, "content": "所以要把拉蒙 換成希洛 會比較好一些摟", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:12:23.899000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204429502793383977", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "拉蒙娜，雷亞，艾繼絲，莉莉\n勝在穩定", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:12:50.684000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204429750802849802", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "希洛，雷亞，艾繼絲，莉莉\n要控制好牌，可以一次爆發直接打死Boss\n但是關鍵在第二次的報償打擊，要多久才能滿", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:13:49.814000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204429891601301535", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且主要，拉蒙娜不會跟雷亞搶胚胎", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:14:23.383000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204430119326711828", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "艾繼絲的狂氣，只是危機時候放（我通常選擇，他準備丟反擊時候，控制他）\n\n這樣我多一回合，回覆耐力", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:15:17.677000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204430185164832850", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後再下一回合，直接打入第二階段", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:15:33.374000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204430520428003368", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後第二階段他丟反擊，就只能硬吃反擊\n\n不過我一般除了，艾繼絲的攻擊\n\n其他，攻擊全賣了，\n詛咒造物：無盡（刪卡+力量的，可以拿來用）", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:16:53.307000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1204431264871092224", "channel_id": "1203195064474669106", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "詛咒造物：殘缺面孔（+1算力，狂氣+30）\n\n除非，你有拿到籌算，增加算力那些\n\n這個會很好用，不然會很卡手", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T14:19:50.796000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203195064474669106", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "血肉_莉莉好好玩（融災普5）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
